Deprecated API

Contents

  • Deprecated Methods
  • Deprecated Constructors
  • Deprecated Methods 
    Method and Description
    org.alljoyn.about.AboutServiceImpl.addAnnouncementHandler(AnnouncementHandler)
    use AboutService.addAnnouncementHandler(AnnouncementHandler handler, String[] interfaces) instead. This function has been deprecated please change your code to use the new addAnnouncementHandler where you specify the interface(s) that you are interested finding. Using this member function could have significant impact on network performance.
    org.alljoyn.services.common.ClientBaseImpl.getObjectClass() 
    org.alljoyn.about.AboutServiceImpl.removeAnnouncementHandler(AnnouncementHandler)
    use AboutService.removeAnnouncementHandler(AnnouncementHandler handler, String[] interfaces) instead.
    org.alljoyn.bus.SessionListener.sessionLost(int)
    Use SessionListener.sessionLost(int,int).
